  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "If I run tests with `buidler-ganache` and call `wallet.provider.getWallets()` , the tests are failing with this error:\r\n\r\n```\r\nError: This method only works with Buidler EVM.\r\nYou can use `await bre.ethers.signers()` in other networks.\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen how one can reveal private keys? \r\n\r\nAccording to [documentation](https://buidler.dev/plugins/nomiclabs-buidler-ganache.html#configuration) the `accounts` option is not supported. Is there a reason for that?",
